---
// About.astro - About Us section with dark woody theme
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden bg-wood-950 border-t border-wood-900/20">
  <!-- Decorative Background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-1/3 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,rgba(181,128,85,0.05),transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-width-container mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-center relative z-10 w-full">
    <!-- Left Column: Image with premium styling -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 order-2 lg:order-1 relative">
      <!-- Decorative background frames -->
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 border border-gold-500/10 rounded-xl pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute -inset-2 border border-wood-500/10 rounded-lg pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div class="relative aspect-square w-full rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-gold-500/20 shadow-2xl group">
        <img
          src="/images/about-barber-work.png"
          alt="Barber working meticulously on a beard"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover transform scale-100 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-wood-950 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-30 pointer-events-none"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: Story & Vision -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 order-1 lg:order-2 flex flex-col space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.25em] text-gold-500 font-bold uppercase block">Nuestra Esencia</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-wood-50">
          Tallando Carácter <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-400 to-wood-300">Desde Hace Más de una Década</span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-wood-200 font-light leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          El Roble nació como un refugio para el hombre moderno que valora el peso de la tradición. En un mundo que se mueve cada vez más rápido, creamos un santuario donde la prisa se queda afuera, las navajas se afilan a mano y la precisión es ley.
        </p>
        <p>
          Inspirados en los clubes de caballeros británicos del siglo XIX, nuestro espacio combina la robustez de la madera de roble con el brillo del bronce y la calidez del cuero. Aquí, cada servicio es una experiencia personalizada, acompañada de un trato impecable, buen café o un excelente whisky single malt.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Core Pillars -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-6">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded bg-wood-900 border border-gold-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-gold-400">
            <!-- Beard / Blade icon -->
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.828 10.172a4 4 0 00-5.656 0l-4 4a4 4 0 105.656 5.656l1.102-1.101m-.758-4.899a4 4 0 005.656 0l4-4a4 4 0 00-5.656-5.656l-1.1 1.1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xs tracking-widest text-wood-50 uppercase font-semibold">Navaja a Mano Alzada</h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-wood-300 font-light mt-1">El afeitado tradicional con toalla caliente y navaja de barbero.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded bg-wood-900 border border-gold-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-gold-400">
            <!-- Gold star icon -->
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xs tracking-widest text-wood-50 uppercase font-semibold">Cuidado Premium</h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-wood-300 font-light mt-1">Utilizamos únicamente óleos y pomadas de manufactura artesanal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
